{"tid":1320484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"上山求籤問香港困局","createTime":"2019-07-15T11:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T03:36:14.000Z","uid":154793,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"557614b82e9afd335f060c5832cb0123d42f9321","tid":1320484,"uid":154793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"上山求籤問吓觀音香港困局求到上籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望靈啦！好人一生平安🙏<br />\n希望呢件事真係可以有好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再有生命犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第十八籤<br />\n<br />\n上籤。卯宮<br />\n<br />\n籤詩版本一<br />\n<br />\n金烏西墜兔東臨<br />\n日夜循環恒古今<br />\n僧道得之無不利<br />\n工商農士各開心<br />\n<br />\n籤詩版本二<br />\n<br />\n金烏西墜兔東昇<br />\n日夜循環至古今<br />\n僧道得知無不利<br />\n士農工商各從心<br />\n<br />\n此卦陰陽消長之象。凡事遂意之兆也。<br />\n<br />\n解  曰<br />\n<br />\n心中無事。所作有功。如弓上箭。一發當空。<br />\n<br />\n世間的事情將之分為兩類，一者代號稱「陰」，另者代號稱「陽」。此籤代表屬「陰」者開始走揚。<br />\n<br />\n譬如；<br />\n<br />\n以性別而言，女性有利，男性則不利。<br />\n<br />\n追求屬於內在靈性等無形者有利，反之追求屬於金錢、物質等有形者不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n職位屬下層者有利，職位屬首長者不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其餘依此類推"},{"pid":"551948d66ebb04ec1b2f294bd043ab4c11b8303e","tid":1320484,"uid":177152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"69cb09b025290b33aa9a040e0b188acf1dbc57c1","tid":1320484,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日夜循環恒古今</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改朝換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82970d6d1bcbd7e04899c92e838d98e3bf02ab1","tid":1320484,"uid":154793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69cb09b025290b33aa9a040e0b188acf1dbc57c1","tid":1320484,"uid":7